*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM init_auth.

* Check User can execute C function
  AUTHORITY-CHECK OBJECT &apos;S_C_FUNCT&apos;
                  ID &apos;ACTVT&apos; FIELD &apos;16&apos;
                  ID &apos;CFUNCNAME&apos; FIELD &apos; &apos;
                  ID &apos;PROGRAM&apos; FIELD &apos;ZAL11&apos;.
