* If not allowed, it is not possible to :
* - Compress/uncompress
* - Create folder
* - Move file/folder
* - Duplicate file/folder
* - Rename file/folder
* - Delete file/folder
* - CHMOD
    CLEAR : s_auth-zip,
            s_auth-unzip,
            s_auth-create_folder,
            s_auth-move_file,
            s_auth-move_folder,
            s_auth-duplicate_file,
            s_auth-duplicate_folder,
            s_auth-rename_file,
            s_auth-rename_folder,
            s_auth-delete_file,
            s_auth-delete_folder,
